    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a meticulously maintained example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. The engine\u2019s eight individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response, pulling cleanly to the 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a Variable M Differential Lock. This vehicle features the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry remains composed under heavy lateral loads. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator refurbishment, addressing the platform's critical vulnerabilities. While showing minor signs of use, the mechanical integrity and drivetrain synchromesh remain excellent.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
