    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i is a stunning example of a well-maintained luxury SUV, offering a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The Deep Sea Blue Metallic exterior remains vibrant and glossy, with only a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with careful highway driving. The vehicle sits on 19-inch star-spoke wheels wrapped in premium tires with significant tread life remaining. Inside, the Canberra Beige Dakota leather interior is in excellent shape; the seats are supple and free of tears, showing only slight, natural creasing on the driver's side bolster. All cabin tech\u2014including the high-resolution navigation system, 360-degree parking cameras, and the panoramic moonroof\u2014operates perfectly. Mechanically, this X5 is top-tier. It comes with a complete, documented service history from certified technicians, including a recent oil service and a fresh set of brake pads. The engine runs smoothly and the 8-speed transmission shifts imperceptibly. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled garage, making it a reliable and sophisticated choice for any discerning buyer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
